]], Serbia\n*{{flagicon|GER}} [[Meissen]], Germany\n*{{flagicon|GRC}} [[Mytilene]], Greece\n*{{flagicon|CYP}} [[Paphos]], Cyprus\n*{{flagicon|ALB}} [[Sarand\u00eb]], Albania\n*{{flagicon|CYP}} [[Tremetousia]], Cyprus\n*{{flagicon|GER}} [[Troisdorf]], Germany\n*{{flagicon|GRC}} [[Vathy, Samos|Vathy]], Greece\n{{div col end}}\n\n==D==\n'''[[Drama, Greece|Drama]]'''<ref>{{cite web |title=\u0391\u03b4\u03b5\u03bb\u03c6\u03bf\u03c0\u03bf\u03af\u03b7\u03c3\u03b7 \u0394\u03c1\u03ac\u03bc\u03b1 \u2013 Lauf|url=https://dimos-dramas.gr/adelfopiisi-drama-lauf/|website=dimos-dramas.gr|publisher=Drama|language=el|accessdate=2020-01-11}}</ref>\n{{div col|colwidth=20em}}\n*{{flagicon|GER}} [[Lauf an der Pegnitz]], Germany\n{{div col end}}\n\n==E==\n'''[[Eleusis]]'''<ref>{{cite web |title=I gemellaggi di Gela: Eleusi, Nordkapp e Wittingen|url=https://gela.italiani.it/i-gemellaggi-di-gela-eleusi-nordkapp-e-wittingen/|website=gela.italiani.it|publisher=Gela|language=it|date=2019-06-11|accessdate=2020-01-10}}</ref>\n*{{flagicon|ITA}} [[Gela]], Italy\n\n==H==\n'''[[Heraklion]]'''<ref>{{cite web |title=Ora\u0219e \u00eenfr\u0103\u021bite|url=http://www.primaria-constanta.ro/oras/orase-infratite|website=primaria-constanta.ro|publisher=Constan\u021ba|language=ro|accessdate=2020-01-10}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=\u0411\u0440\u0430\u0442\u0438\u043c\u0459\u0435\u045a\u0435 \u0427\u0443\u043a\u0430\u0440\u0438\u0446\u0435 \u0438 \u0418\u0440\u0430\u043a\u043b\u0438\u043e\u043d\u0430|url=http://athens.mfa.gov.rs/cir/newstext.php?subaction=showfull&id=1549959929|website=athens.mfa.gov.rs|publisher=Serbian Embassy in Athens|language=sr|date=2019-02-12|accessdate=2020-01-10}}</ref><ref name=limassol>{{cite web |title=Twinned Cities|url=https://www.limassolmunicipal.com.cy/en/didimopoiimenes-poleis|website=limassolmunicipal.com.cy|publisher=Limassol|accessdate=2020-01-10}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Sister Cities|url=https://www.tampagov.net/city-clerk/sister-cities|website=tampagov.net|publis