]], Serbia\n*{{flagicon|GER}} [[Maintal]], Germany\n*{{flagicon|AUT}} [[Moosburg, Austria|Moosburg]], Austria\n*{{flagicon|RUS}} [[Surgut]], Russia\n{{div col end}}\n\n'''[[Kavala]]'''<ref>{{cite web |title=\u0391\u03b4\u03b5\u03bb\u03c6\u03ad\u03c2 \u03c0\u03cc\u03bb\u03b5\u03b9\u03c2|url=https://kavala.gov.gr/o-dimos/o-dimos-xthes-kai-simera/adelfes-polis|website=kavala.gov.gr|publisher=Kavala|language=el|accessdate=2020-01-09}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Kavala, Greece|url=https://www.sistercities-durham.com/kavala-greece|website=sistercities-durham.com|publisher=Sister Cities of Durham|accessdate=2020-01-09}}</ref>\n{{div col|colwidth=20em}}\n*{{flagicon|SRB}} [[Aran\u0111elovac]], Serbia\n*{{flagicon|USA}} [[Durham, North Carolina|Durham]], United States\n*{{flagicon|BIH}} [[Gradi\u0161ka, Bosnia and Herzegovina|Gradi\u0161ka]], Bosnia and Herzegovina\n*{{flagicon|GER}} [[Nuremberg]], Germany\n*{{flagicon|ESP}} [[Taranc\u00f3n]], Spain\n<!--rest - not twinning or twinning ended-->\n{{div col end}}\n\n'''[[Keratsini]]'''<ref>{{cite web |title=\u03a3\u03c4\u03c1\u03b1\u03c4\u03b7\u03b3\u03b9\u03ba\u03cc \u03a3\u03c7\u03ad\u03b4\u03b9\u03bf \u0394\u03ae\u03bc\u03bf\u03c5 \u039a\u03b5\u03c1\u03b1\u03c4\u03c3\u03b9\u03bd\u03af\u03bf\u03c5 \u2013 \u0394\u03c1\u03b1\u03c0\u03b5\u03c4\u03c3\u03ce\u03bd\u03b1\u03c2 2015-2019|url=https://keratsini-drapetsona.gr/images/pdf/Epixeirisiaka_sxedia/A_meros_stratigiko_sxedio_2015_2019.pdf|website=keratsini-drapetsona.gr|publisher=Keratsini|page=186|language=el|accessdate=2020-01-11}}</ref>\n*{{flagicon|SVK}} [[Pre\u0161ov]], Slovakia\n\n'''[[Kolindros]]''' is a member of the ''Charter of European Rural Communities'', a [[town twinning]] association across the [[European Union]], alongside with:<ref>{{cite web |title=Charter members|url=https://www.europeancharter.eu/chartermembers/|website=europeancharter.eu|publisher=Charter of European Rural Communities|accessdate=2020-01-10}}</ref>\n{{div col|colwidth=20em}}\n*{{flagicon|ES