, Greece|Oia]], Greece\n*{{flagicon|GRC}} [[Plomari]], Greece\n*{{flagicon|FRA}} [[Quimper]], France\n{{div col end}}\n\n'''[[Lefkada (city)|Lefkada]]'''<ref>{{cite web |title=\u0391\u03b4\u03b5\u03bb\u03c6\u03bf\u03c0\u03bf\u03b9\u03b7\u03bc\u03ad\u03bd\u03b5\u03c2 \u03a0\u03cc\u03bb\u03b5\u03b9\u03c2|url=http://www.lefkada.gov.gr/Default.aspx?tabid=559|website=lefkada.gov.gr|publisher=Lefkada|language=el|accessdate=2020-01-09}}</ref>\n{{div col|colwidth=20em}}\n*{{flagicon|SWE}} [[Emmaboda Municipality|Emmaboda]], Sweden\n*{{flagicon|FRA}} [[Leucate]], France\n*{{flagicon|ISR}} [[Nahariya]], Israel\n*{{flagicon|CYP}} [[Paralimni]], Cyprus\n*{{flagicon|ROU}} [[Ploie\u0219ti]], Romania\n*{{flagicon|UKR}} [[Odessa|Prymorsky District (Odessa)]], Ukraine\n*{{flagicon|JPN}} [[Shinjuku|Shinjuku (Tokyo)]], Japan\n<!--Str\u00e1\u017enice - inactive-->\n{{div col end}}\n\n==M==\n'''[[Mouresi]]'''<ref name=magnesia/>\n{{div col|colwidth=20em}}\n*{{flagicon|CYP}} [[Aradippou]], Cyprus\n*{{flagicon|ALB}} [[Mollaj|Mollaj (Korc\u00eb)]], Albania\n{{div col end}}\n\n'''[[Mytilene]]'''<ref name=mytilene>{{cite web |title=\u0391\u03b4\u03b5\u03bb\u03c6\u03bf\u03c0\u03bf\u03b9\u03b7\u03bc\u03ad\u03bd\u03b5\u03c2 \u03a0\u03cc\u03bb\u03b5\u03b9\u03c2|url=http://www.mytilene.gr/%CE%B4%CE%AE%CE%BC%CE%BF%CF%82-%CE%BC%CF%85%CF%84%CE%B9%CE%BB%CE%AE%CE%BD%CE%B7%CF%82/%CE%B1%CE%B4%CE%B5%CE%BB%CF%86%CE%BF%CF%80%CE%BF%CE%B9%CE%B7%CE%BC%CE%AD%CE%BD%CE%B5%CF%82-%CF%80%CF%8C%CE%BB%CE%B5%CE%B9%CF%82/|website=mytilene.gr|publisher=Mytilene|language=el|accessdate=2020-01-09}}</ref>\n{{div col|colwidth=20em}}\n*{{flagicon|BIH}} [[Brod, Bosnia and Herzegovina|Brod]], Bosnia and Herzegovina\n*{{flagicon|GRC}} [[Corfu (city)|Corfu]], Greece\n*{{flagicon|GRE}} [[Kalamaria]], Greece\n*{{flagicon|GRC}} [[Lamia (city)|Lamia]], Greece\n*{{flagicon|CYP}} [[Paphos]], Cyprus\n*{{flagicon|USA}} [[Portland, Maine|Portland]], United States\n*{{flagicon|GRC}} [[Preveza]], Greece\n*{{flagicon|JPN}} [[Setouchi, Okaya