 has five twin cities in the world|url=https://www.ekapija.com/en/news/2162335/belgrade-has-five-twin-cities-in-the-world|website=ekapija.com|publisher=Belgrade|date=2018-06-18|accessdate=2020-01-11}}</ref><ref name=mytilene/>\n{{div col|colwidth=20em}}\n*{{flagicon|CYP}} [[Asha, Cyprus|Asha]], Cyprus\n*{{flagicon|MNE}} [[Bar Municipality|Bar]], Montenegro\n*{{flagicon|ITA}} [[Bari]], Italy \n*{{flagicon|SRB}} [[Belgrade]], Serbia\n*{{flagicon|USA}} [[Bethlehem, Pennsylvania|Bethlehem]], United States\n*{{flagicon|ITA}} [[Brindisi]], Italy\n*{{flagicon|ITA}} [[Carovigno]], Italy\n*{{flagicon|CYP}} [[Famagusta]], Cyprus\n*{{flagicon|GRC}} [[Ioannina]], Greece\n*{{flagicon|SVN}} [[Koper]], Slovenia\n*{{flagicon|SRB}} [[Kru\u0161evac]], Serbia\n*{{flagicon|GER}} [[Meissen]], Germany\n*{{flagicon|GRC}} [[Mytilene]], Greece\n*{{flagicon|CYP}} [[Paphos]], Cyprus\n*{{flagicon|ALB}} [[Sarand\u00eb]], Albania\n*{{flagicon|CYP}} [[Tremetousia]], Cyprus\n*{{flagicon|GER}} [[Troisdorf]], Germany\n*{{flagicon|GRC}} [[Vathy, Samos|Vathy]], Greece\n{{div col end}}\n\n==D==\n'''[[Drama, Greece|Drama]]'''<ref>{{cite web |title=\u0391\u03b4\u03b5\u03bb\u03c6\u03bf\u03c0\u03bf\u03af\u03b7\u03c3\u03b7 \u0394\u03c1\u03ac\u03bc\u03b1 \u2013 Lauf|url=https://dimos-dramas.gr/adelfopiisi-drama-lauf/|website=dimos-dramas.gr|publisher=Drama|language=el|accessdate=2020-01-11}}</ref>\n{{div col|colwidth=20em}}\n*{{flagicon|GER}} [[Lauf an der Pegnitz]], Germany\n{{div col end}}\n\n==E==\n'''[[Eleusis]]'''<ref>{{cite web |title=I gemellaggi di Gela: Eleusi, Nordkapp e Wittingen|url=https://gela.italiani.it/i-gemellaggi-di-gela-eleusi-nordkapp-e-wittingen/|website=gela.italiani.it|publisher=Gela|language=it|date=2019-06-11|accessdate=2020-01-10}}</ref>\n*{{flagicon|ITA}} [[Gela]], Italy\n\n==H==\n'''[[Heraklion]]'''<ref>{{cite web |title=Ora\u0219e \u00eenfr\u0103\u021bite|url=http://www.primaria-constanta.ro/oras/orase-infratite|website=primaria-constanta.ro|publisher=Constan\u021ba|language=ro|